snippet.title: Hexle 🧩 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Hexle is an original take on Sudoku with hexadecimal numbers and binary restrictions. It's got infinite puzzles, daily challenges, weekly megaboards and plenty of color palettes to unlock!

🧠 Get Hexle on Itch: https://punkcake.itch.io/hexle
🤔 Get Hexle on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2672770/Hexle/
💬 Join our community on Discord: https://discord.gg/dpQx647USm
